Bomber will be:
        dedicated to Jenn
        a bomberman clone
        multi platform
        event based
        multiplayer (local, network later)
        flexible as far as clients go
        a way for me to learn more python

Plan:
        output a map
        load a map
        add a player
        spawn a player
        move a player
        drop a bomb
        explode a bomb
        blow up a wall
        kill a player
        upgrade player

